Interface FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator.StreamTransformTranslator<Type extends PTransform>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator

    public static interface FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator.StreamTransformTranslator<Type extends PTransform>
    The interface that every Flink translator of a Beam operator should implement. This interface is for streaming jobs. For examples of such translators see FlinkStreamingTransformTranslators.
